So we wanna preserve the cart between page loads.

04:19.560 --> 04:20.400
That's what I'm getting at.

04:20.400 --> 04:22.960
So we're gonna use context to do that.

04:22.960 --> 04:25.960
Now, really what you could do,

04:25.960 --> 04:28.640
